      "system": {
        "description": "<p><strong>Change form: </strong>At will; takes 1 round:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Humanoid: </strong>Standard form.</li>\n<li><strong style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\">Dire wolf:</strong><span style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\"> Att 1 &times; bite (2d4), MV </span>150&rsquo; (50&rsquo;). AC, HD, morale, saves as vampire.</li>\n<li><strong style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\">Giant bat:</strong><span style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\"> Att 1 &times; bite (1d4), MV </span>30&rsquo; (10&rsquo;) / 180&rsquo; (60&rsquo;) flying. AC, HD, morale, saves as vampire.</li>\n<li><strong style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\">Gaseous cloud:</strong><span style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\"> MV 180&rsquo; (60&rsquo;) </span>flying. Immune to all weapons. Cannot attack.</li>\n</ul>",
